CustomField.description: Use with the end date to calculate the Availability End Date/Time value. Must be a string like "12:00 AM". Will be interpreted in timezone of user executing process.
CustomField.inlineHelpText: Use with the end date to calculate the Availability End Date/Time value. Must be a string like "11:59 PM". Will be interpreted in timezone of user executing process.
CustomField.label: Availability End Time
